item.title: [HIVE-21625] Fix TxnIdUtils.checkEquivalentWriteIds, also provides a comparison method
item.description: TxnIdUtils.checkEquivalentWriteIds has a bug which thinks ({1,2,3,4}, 6) and ({1,2,3,4,5,6}, 8) compatible (the notation is (invalidlist, hwm)). Here is a patch to fix it, also provide a comparison method to check which is newer.
item.summary: Fix TxnIdUtils.checkEquivalentWriteIds, also provides a comparison method

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
